data.description: Come check out this beautiful brick 3 bedroom 2 bath home located in small town Wetumpka. Situated on a spacious half acre lot with plenty of room to spread out. This home offers over 2,000 square feet of living space and a large attached double car garage. An open floor plan with a lovely fireplace in the living area overlooking the kitchen. The kitchen offers a small breakfast nook with a formal dining room just off the main entry door. Split floor plan with master and laundry room just inside the garage entry and bedrooms 2 and 3 share a bathroom off the living space. You'll love this covered back porch, perfect for entertaining guests in the back yard! Nice out in the country feel without being too far from town! Don't miss out on this one, call your favorite realtor today to schedule a private showing!
